lead_paragraph: Barcelona take a 32-match unbeaten run to Arsenal for the first leg of their Champions League last 16 tie on Tuesday as the Catalans continue their bid to become the first team to retain the trophy in 26 years.

headline.print_headline: Barca Continue Title Defence at Old Foes Arsenal
